== 發行 ==
2014年10月，演員[[奧利維亞·魏爾德|奧利維亞·魏爾德]]、[[路克·伊凡斯|路克·伊凡斯]]、[[艾米·漢默|艾米·漢默]]、[[席尼·墨菲|席尼·墨菲]]與{{le|麥克·史麥利|Michael Smiley}}加入本片的陣容，由[[班·懷特利|班·懷特利]]擔任導演，並與艾美·江普共同撰寫劇本。電影為懷特利和監製安迪·史塔克的Rook Films公司製作。{{le|Film4 Productions|Film4 Productions}}也會參與電影的製作和出資<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/luke-evans-to-star-in-ben-wheatleys-free-fire-1201338287/|title=Luke Evans to Star in Ben Wheatley’s ‘Free Fire’|website=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]]|first=Leo|last=Barraclough|date=2014-10-24|accessdate=2016-08-01|archive-date=2016-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160610133005/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/luke-evans-to-star-in-ben-wheatleys-free-fire-1201338287/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年4月，[[布麗·拉爾森|布麗·拉森]]加入取代魏爾德，因魏爾德的行程與本片有所衝突<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/brie-larson-free-fire-cast-olivia-wilde-ben-wheatley-1201468099/|title=Brie Larson Joins Cast of Ben Wheatley’s ‘Free Fire’ (EXCLUSIVE)|website=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|first=Justin|last=Kroll|date=2015-04-07|accessdate=2016-08-01|archive-date=2016-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160818060025/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/brie-larson-free-fire-cast-olivia-wilde-ben-wheatley-1201468099/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而伊凡斯也同樣因故退出。

=== 拍攝 ===
正式拍攝於2015年6月8日在[[東薩塞克斯郡|東薩塞克斯郡]]的[[布萊頓|布萊頓]]開始進行<ref>{{cite news|last1=Jagernauth|first1=Kevin|title=Ben Wheatley's 'Free Fire' Starts Filming, Full Cast Confirmed|url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/ben-wheatleys-free-fire-starts-filming-full-cast-confirmed-20150609|accessdate=2015-06-13|work=indiewire.com|date=2015-06-09|archive-date=2015-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150609213844/http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/ben-wheatleys-free-fire-starts-filming-full-cast-confirmed-20150609|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Jaafar|first1=Ali|title=Ben Wheatley’s ‘Free Fire’ Rounds Out Cast: Jack Reynor, Sam Riley And Noah Taylor All On Board|url=http://deadline.com/2015/06/ben-wheatley-free-fire-jack-reynor-sam-riley-noah-taylor-martin-scorsese-armie-hammer-cillian-murphy-1201439919/|accessdate=2015-06-13|work=deadline.com|date=2015-06-09|archive-date=2015-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150613171458/http://deadline.com/2015/06/ben-wheatley-free-fire-jack-reynor-sam-riley-noah-taylor-martin-scorsese-armie-hammer-cillian-murphy-1201439919/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。拍攝直到2015年7月17日宣布結束<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ssninsider.com/on-the-set-for-72015-daniel-radcliffe-starts-shooting-swiss-army-men-meryl-streep-finishes-florence-foster-jenkins/|title=On the Set for 7/20/15: Daniel Radcliffe Starts Shooting ‘Swiss Army Men’, Meryl Streep Finishes ‘Florence Foster Jenkins’|website=SSN Insider|date=2015-07-20|accessdate=2016-08-07|archive-date=2015-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150723005058/http://www.ssninsider.com/on-the-set-for-72015-daniel-radcliffe-starts-shooting-swiss-army-men-meryl-streep-finishes-florence-foster-jenkins/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

